<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Deep calls to deep at the noise of your waterfalls;</para>

<para style="q1">all your waves and your billows have gone over me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Yet Yahweh will command his covenant faithfulness in the daytime;</para>

<para style="q1">in the night his song will be with me,</para>

<para style="q1">a prayer to the God of my life.</para>
